subject: College Athletics
Colleges and Universities
lead_paragraph: Julian Rauch’s 24-yard field goal with 26 seconds left put Appalachian State ahead of Michigan and Corey Lynch’s blocked field goal in the final seconds sealed one of college football’s biggest upsets.
